afe.memory.access=allow and -Dio.netty.tryReflectionSetAccessible=true for 5.0.1 / Netty 4.2.x on JDK 25.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"OAuth2WebClient classes are present but depend on optional Vert.x OAuth2 support; avoid targeting OAuth2-specific APIs unless adding the optional oauth2 dependency is intentionally in scope.\",\n    \"Local Gradle and Native Image verification remain authoritative; if Netty changes in later Vert.x 5.0.x versions, the unsafe workaround may need revalidation.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0a7f7113e6d13d7d016a3ed09a9d988197a277ff70ea0a47c4\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 3090, "output": 792, "cacheRead": 25088, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 28970, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782501520783, "responseId": "resp_0a7f7113e6d13d7d016a3ed0913df88197b3ade0293433cfba"}}
